<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9457</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18516</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“伊坦，等等！” 尼娜叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18516</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20840</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她跑向伊坦。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20840</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24395</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你为什么穿冬天的外套？” 她问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24395</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27733</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “雪莉老师说我们要去外面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27733</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31462</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>外面很冷！” 伊坦说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31462</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34044</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “现在才十月！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34044</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37321</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>等到一月就真的冷了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37321</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48571</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜想想就发抖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48571</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52092</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “在门口排队。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52092</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59464</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们要去树林走走。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59464</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63490</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “今天的手工需要四片秋叶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63490</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69022</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小心地把秋叶放进你的纸袋里。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69022</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要找红色的。” 莉琪说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72501</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74456</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“枫叶很美。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74456</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76787</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要各种颜色。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76787</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>橙色、红色、黄色、棕色。” 尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84917</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87924</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “真棒。” 伊坦说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87924</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90454</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也要各种颜色。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90454</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92567</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>  “有棕色？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92567</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96030</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>棕色太丑了。” 莉琪说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96030</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98889</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我才不用棕色的叶子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98889</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102459</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> 她追上雪莉老师。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102459</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111509</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“和你的男朋友玩儿得开心。” 她对尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111895</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119545</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “这片叶子好像一把扇子！” 伊坦说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119545</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123316</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他用黄色的叶子给尼娜扇风。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123316</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126534</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “哈哈，真的呢。” 尼娜说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126534</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129533</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们用这些叶子做什么呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129533</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134587</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要做窗户的装饰。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134587</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139454</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “首先，我们把叶子放在蜡纸里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139454</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145258</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后我们用线把它们挂起来。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145258</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148857</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“听上去很简单。” 贾森说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148857</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152527</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “听上去很好玩儿！” 尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152527</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156065</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把叶子放在一张蜡纸上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156065</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160036</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>要让他们至少间隔四厘米。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163392</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后在上面放另一张蜡纸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163392</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166715</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>做好以后，来我这里排队。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166715</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171722</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我用熨斗熨一下。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171722</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179526</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “太好了。” 莉琪看着她的叶子说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179526</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182677</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“全是红色的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182677</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186934</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “莉琪，你的叶子很漂亮。” 尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186934</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189774</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是莉琪没有理尼娜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189774</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194923</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她走到雪莉老师那里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194923</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200999</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我做好了。” 她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201471</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204451</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>下一个是尼娜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210259</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师小心地把尼娜的蜡纸放在熨烫板上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210259</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214449</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她盖上一张旧布开始熨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214449</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218091</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你和莉琪没事吧？” 她小声问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218091</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221793</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜的眼睛里充满了泪水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221793</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224166</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她摇摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224166</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227478</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “怎么了？” 雪莉老师问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227478</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230812</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “莉琪今天对我很不友好。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230812</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235151</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我不知道为什么！” 尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235151</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237822</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “你和伊坦关系很好。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237822</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242948</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可能她觉得被忽视了。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242948</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248372</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，莉琪是我最好的朋友！” 尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248372</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253584</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她可能需要时间来适应伊坦。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253584</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256413</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把叶子给尼娜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256413</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258211</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“给你。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258211</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260243</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你的叶子很好看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260243</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264184</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过几分钟，我们要把它们剪下来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266263</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271199</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “沿着叶子的形状剪下来。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271199</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274388</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森和莉琪剪了圆形。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274388</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278861</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比和伊坦沿着叶子的形状剪下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278861</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281541</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜剪了正方形。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281541</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284931</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她还在想雪莉老师的话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284931</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288399</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪嫉妒伊坦吗？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288399</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291771</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “现在在下面打一个孔。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291771</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后用一条长线把叶子穿起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301592</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后在线的两边打结。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301592</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>306905</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>  “现在可以挂起来了吗？” 尼娜问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>306905</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>317128</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “莉琪，把你的挂在我的上面吧！” 尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>317128</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>321588</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> 莉琪跳起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>321588</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>326392</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的彩色叶子好像也很不错。” 她笑着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>326392</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>330417</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜对自己最好的朋友笑了笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>330417</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>332888</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她喜欢交新朋友。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>332888</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>344133</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但她也不想失去自己的老朋友。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>